Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "XIX Chapeau de paille"

  • Draft text: "Chapeau de Paille von Rubens"
  • Extracts from different publications about Rubens' family and the 'Portrait of Susanna Lunden' (called 'Le Chapeau de Paille')
  • Various correspondence about 'Le Chapeau de Paille' dated 1943
